<L>__{exterior echo park (downtown l.a.) day}
<A>__{john sits at a park bench. motionless. taking in the world. clouds passing the sun. shadows drifting across the city. leaves swirling after passing cars. john just sits there, hearing every breath he takes, wondering which one will be his last.}
<C>__{ellie }
<D>__{lung cancer? lung cancer?!}
<A>__{john turns to see ellie (23) strutting up the sidewalk. uninhibited. oozing sex appeal. but dangerous. in more ways than you think.}
