<A>__{ellie sits back down, strokes his arm.}
<C>__{ellie}
<D>__{have you gone to see the snob?}
<A>__{like scratching fingers across a blackboard. no way.}
<C>__{ellie}
<D>__{look, don't let your ego get in the way on this. i'd miss having someone up here i can... relate to.}
<A>__{she gives him a kiss. and for a second john's leg is brushed by a tail. john doesn't react. just turns and walks away.}
